.RE

.sp
.ne 2
.mk
.na
\fB\fBEX_NOUSER\fR\fR
.ad
.RS 18n
.rt  
User name not recognized.
.RE

.sp
.ne 2
.mk
.na
\fB\fBEX_UNAVAILABLE\fR\fR
.ad
.RS 18n
.rt  
